 49, was accused of launching a complaint about the Pratt-themed cookies at Vicente Foods, a staple grocery store in Brentwood.", "large_image": "xFXljwm4ZaUMeJQO.png", "title": "Jimmy Kimmel's sister-in-law 'bullied business over Spencer Pratt'"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsZASR3h", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 35, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8634691, "raw_content": "", "author": "blvntbr", "created": 1779490525715, "profile_picture": "VKosve2FUDhO", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "OpusX", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "www.thearmorylife.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsZASR3h.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://www.thearmorylife.com/taking-the-pig-for-a-walk-history-of-the-m60/", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Taking the Pig for a Walk: History of the M60", "last_comment_created": 1779499483993, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 10, "score_up": 35, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "I was six feet tall and 163 lbs. without a gram of extraneous body fat. Though I didn\u2019t enjoy it, I did a weekly 10k run with my mates in boots with a rucksack and M16. I was in the best physical condition of my life and believed myself to be both bulletproof and immortal. Read More", "large_image": "hgbCNDs4Tg8oqi2p.png", "title": "Taking the Pig for a Walk: History of the M60 - The Armory Life"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsZASypA", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 25, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8634844, "raw_content": "This place has shown its fractures. Accountability, integrity, and grit were a demand of MAGA Pede's. There has been a lot of winning, and a lot of letdowns. This place has been infiltrated by bots, MIGA, and other bad faith FAGGOTS. The Mods have let too much shit slide. Various ideas have been put forward to fix problems with infiltrators/shills, but nothing has been implemented. I've check this place almost every day for the last 7 years. I see a lot of posts that belong somewhere else and not here. I've seen plenty of bad faith posters trying to stir up shit.\n\nFor those of you who are MAGA, and want any calling themselves MAGA to be accountable to what MAGA is, and not just yes men, respect. I think a lot of us have learned that not everyone here is MAGA, and come here with an ulterior agenda. To those FAGGOTS, when I see you, I block you.\n\nAlso to those who've been here the last 7 years, here's to many more.", "author": "Emperorvoid", "created": 1779496983646, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "wunderwaffen", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "7 Years, and this place has changed.", "last_comment_created": 1779503578518, "content": "<p>This place has shown its fractures. Accountability, integrity, and grit were a demand of MAGA Pede's. There has been a lot of winning, and a lot of letdowns. This place has been infiltrated by bots, MIGA, and other bad faith FAGGOTS. The Mods have let too much shit slide. Various ideas have been put forward to fix problems with infiltrators/shills, but nothing has been implemented. I've check this place almost every day for the last 7 years. I see a lot of posts that belong somewhere else and not here. I've seen plenty of bad faith posters trying to stir up shit.</p>\n<p>For those of you who are MAGA, and want any calling themselves MAGA to be accountable to what MAGA is, and not just yes men, respect. I think a lot of us have learned that not everyone here is MAGA, and come here with an ulterior agenda. To those FAGGOTS, when I see you, I block you.</p>\n<p>Also to those who've been here the last 7 years, here's to many more.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 14, "score_up": 25, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsZASyYj", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 27, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8634809, "raw_content": "", "author": "flp999", "created": 1779495411619, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "DurkaDurkaIMJ", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "nypost.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsZASyYj.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://nypost.com/2026/05/21/real-estate/residents-fume-as-georgia-power-seizes-homes-under-eminent-domain/", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Hundreds of Georgia residents are going to have their homes seized under eminent domain to build a plant to provide electricity for a data center. You have the same amount of rights and protections under Corporatism as you do under Communis